com.knowledgebin.kb

Class Licenses

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.knowledgebin.kb.Licenses

  • class Licenses
extends Object
    This class supports the loading and scanning of licenses for the KBConfig class.

    This class is loaded at application startup and contains a static array userID ranges that are valid.

    TODO: This class should be modified to support dynamic modification of the License table.
